<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich von Feilitzsch, Amtmann zu Hohenberg</head><p>Der Rat bittet für Sebald und Heinrich Imhoff, Bürger zu Nürnberg, um Herausgabe der von Michel Lang geführten drei Fässer mit Kaufmannsware.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_85" id="41r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_85_r1l19"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Veilſche</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l20">Amptman cʒu <expan>hohemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l21">Lieber <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / vns
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt / Sebolt vnd <expan cert="medium">h<ex>einrich</ex></expan> im hof </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l22">
<add>vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan></add> vvie daʒ Jr Jn drew vaſʒ mit
                        kauffmanſchaft dıe der Mıchel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l23">Lang von Eger gefürt hat aufgehalten het / vnd maint </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l24">daʒ dıe auſʒleute <del rend="strikethrough">ſe </del>
                        wern / die Jr Jn <del rend="strikethrough"> doch </del> doch wider </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l26">ledig gelaſſen habt / Alſo / ob <add><ab facs="#facs_85_r1l25">man </ab></add> euch brief von vns bringe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l27">daʒ dıe der <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ſein Alſo / laſſen wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l28"><expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wiſſen / daʒ die
                                <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger dıe
                            <expan>obgeſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l29">drew vaſʒ mit kauffmanſchaft vor vns cʒu den
                                <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l30">behabt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ dıe Jr vnd
                        anderr <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l31">Alſo / daʒ <expan>kh<ex>ein</ex></expan> auſʒman weder
                        teil noch gemeın daran hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r1l32"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_85" id="41r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Veilsche, amptman czu
                                <expan>Hohemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        fürgelegt Sebolt und <expan cert="medium">H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> Im Hof,
                            <add>unser <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan></add>, wie daz ir in drew vasz
                        mit kauffmanschaft, die der Michel Lang von Eger gefürt hat, aufgehalten het
                        und maint, daz die auszleute wern, die ir in doch wider ledig gelassen habt;
                        also ob <add>man</add> euch brief von uns bringe, daz die der
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, sein; also lassen wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wissen, daz die
                                <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        burger, die <expan>obges<ex>chriben</ex></expan> drew vasz mit
                        kauffmanschaft vor uns czu den <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> behabt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz die ir und anderr
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> sein, also daz <expan>kh<ex>ein</ex></expan>
                        auszman weder teil noch gemein daran hab.
                        <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
